  "notes": "Born 1586 in Upwey, Dorset, England. Father: Thomas Brewse (1556-1594, died when Alice was 8). Married Henry Brundish Tewksbury. Husband died 1621 when son Henry was born. Son Henry Tewksbury (1621-1697) emigrated to Massachusetts in 1654. If the death date of 1697 is accurate, Alice lived to approximately 111 years old — extraordinary even by modern standards. Died in Newbury, Essex County, MA. Buried June 29, 1697 at Searby-With-Owmby, Lincolnshire, England."
